# Copy this file to .env and replace the value with your GitHub personal access token.
# Required for npm run test:local and `vercel dev`.
#
# Minimum scopes / permissions:
#   * Classic PAT       — public_repo, read:user. Add read:org to read members of private orgs.
#   * Fine-grained PAT  — Repository access: Public (read-only). For private repos or private
#                         org members, add the relevant private-repo / Organization permissions.
#
# See the README "Setting up your GitHub token" section for the full walkthrough.
GITHUB_TOKEN=your_github_token_here
